    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Now I am dealing with Mac OSX. However I found sometimes this is no sound. People say it&rsquo;s a bug. I have tried some methods. And found this goes for me every time.
```bash</p>

<h1>!/bin/bash</h1>

<p>sudo kextunload /System/Library/Extensions/AppleHDA.kext
sudo kextload /System/Library/Extensions/AppleHDA.kext
```
Put the code into a shell script and run the script whenever the issue occurs.</p>

